headline: EA to Release Third Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Results on February 3, 2026
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., January 13, 2026--Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA) will release its financial results for the fiscal quarter ended December 31, 2025 after the close of market on Tuesday, February 3, 2026.
